Template: coverboy/ha_url
Type: string
Default: http://homeassistant:8123
Description: Home Assistant URL:
 The Home Assistant URL to connect to. For example, http://homeassistant:8123.

Template: coverboy/ha_token
Type: string
Default: long-lived-access-token
Description: Home Assistant Long-Lived Access Token:
 The long-lived access token to use for authentication with Home Assistant.
 This can be generated in the Home Assistant UI under your user profile in the security tab.